---

Note on the auto-update channel:
This software includes an auto-update mechanism (Velopack) that downloads
new versions from the official Orlixys GitHub Releases. Forks intending to
distribute their own builds should reconfigure the update feed to their own
release endpoint to avoid silently substituting their users' installations
with upstream Orlixys releases.
